### Montando ambiente {MacOS}:

- Instalar homebrew:
/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"

- Instalar node:
brew install node

- Instalar Appium

npm i appium
npm i wd

- Instalar Java 8
brew install --cask adoptopenjdk8

- Instalar Maven
brew install maven

